<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Key improvements made:</p>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words"><strong>Structure</strong>:
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words">Added a <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">main()</span> function to organize the execution flow</li>
<li class="break-words">Used <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">readonly</span> for constants</li>
<li class="break-words">Better function organization with clear purposes</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="break-words"><strong>Error Handling</strong>:
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words">Added checks for file/directory readability</li>
<li class="break-words">Redirected error messages to stderr (<span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">&gt;&amp;2</span>)</li>
<li class="break-words">Added trap for script interruption</li>
<li class="break-words">Added error checking for critical operations (mktemp, split, etc.)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="break-words"><strong>Safety</strong>:
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words">Improved temporary directory creation with <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">-t</span> flag</li>
<li class="break-words">Added more robust file existence checks</li>
<li class="break-words">Better quoting of variables to handle spaces in filenames</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="break-words"><strong>Clarity</strong>:
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words">Added more detailed comments</li>
<li class="break-words">Consistent indentation</li>
<li class="break-words">Meaningful variable names</li>
<li class="break-words">Separated log initialization into its own function</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="break-words"><strong>Efficiency</strong>:
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words">Reduced redundant checks</li>
<li class="break-words">Combined some echo statements</li>
<li class="break-words">Used <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">continue</span> instead of nested conditions where appropriate</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">To use this script:</p>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words">Ensure you have write permissions in the current directory</li>
<li class="break-words">Make it executable: <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">chmod +x script.sh</span></li>
<li class="break-words">Run it: <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">./script.sh</span></li>
<li class="break-words">Requires <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">ollama</span> and <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">split</span> commands to be available</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">The script maintains its original functionality while being more robust and maintainable. It processes .txt files, splits them into 100-line chunks, generates summaries using ollama, and tracks progress.</p></div><div class="order-first sticky hidden @xl/mainview:top-0 @[960px]/mainview:block top-12 h-0 opacity-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100 -mt-2 -ml-12 -left-[26px]"><div class="min-h-7 py-4 flex flex-col gap-0.5"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium leading-[normal] cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-default [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:-mx-0.5 text-secondary hover:text-primary hover:bg-button-ghost-hover disabled:hover:text-secondary disabled:hover:bg-inherit h-10 w-10 rounded-full" type="button" data-state="closed"><span style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-[2] size-4"><rect x="3" y="8" width="13" height="13" rx="4" stroke="currentColor"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M13 2.00004L12.8842 2.00002C12.0666 1.99982 11.5094 1.99968 11.0246 2.09611C9.92585 2.31466 8.95982 2.88816 8.25008 3.69274C7.90896 4.07944 7.62676 4.51983 7.41722 5.00004H9.76392C10.189 4.52493 10.7628 4.18736 11.4147 4.05768C11.6802 4.00488 12.0228 4.00004 13 4.00004H14.6C15.7366 4.00004 16.5289 4.00081 17.1458 4.05121C17.7509 4.10066 18.0986 4.19283 18.362 4.32702C18.9265 4.61464 19.3854 5.07358 19.673 5.63807C19.8072 5.90142 19.8994 6.24911 19.9488 6.85428C19.9992 7.47112 20 8.26343 20 9.40004V11C20 11.9773 19.9952 12.3199 19.9424 12.5853C19.8127 13.2373 19.4748 13.8114 19 14.2361V16.5829C20.4795 15.9374 21.5804 14.602 21.9039 12.9755C22.0004 12.4907 22.0002 11.9334 22 11.1158L22 11V9.40004V