<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Changes made:</p>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words">Kept the <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">SUMMARY_FILE</span> constant and all summary generation functionality</li>
<li class="break-words">Added <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">SKIP_FILE="overview.txt"</span> constant</li>
<li class="break-words">Added a check in <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">process_files</span> to skip "overview.txt"</li>
<li class="break-words">Maintained the original summarization process using <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">ollama</span></li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This version will:</p>
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words">Skip processing any file named "overview.txt"</li>
<li class="break-words">Process all other .txt files by splitting them into 100-line chunks</li>
<li class="break-words">Generate summaries for each chunk using <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-sunset/10 text-rust dark:bg-dawn/10 dark:text-dawn">ollama run vanilj/phi-4</span></li>
<li class="break-words">Save summaries to "detailed-summary.txt"</li>
<li class="break-words">Log progress to "progress.log"</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">To use:</p>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
